data.description: Great Charming and Cozy Rambler with 3 Bedrooms, 2 Full baths, with a .168 acre corner lot located in the Palmer Lake Community where you can enjoy water and nature all year long with just a 3 minute walk to the lake. One of the few Stick Built Homes on the Peninsula! This home offers a 2 car garage with an open concept floor plan with a lot of natural light. The Kitchen comes will all appliances and large pantry storage area. Nice deck off of Kitchen with eating space for enjoying those summer barbecues with an on-deck propane hookup option.
